Barebonephp is designed for PHP developers who want to understand what is going on behind most MVC frameworks.
Its stripped-down codes and structures allow developers to improve their understandings of frameworks they use.


Simple Documentation

Controller
	File Name:
		{name}.php
	Class Name:
		{name}_Controller extends Base
	Construct:
		parrent::__construct();	
	Default:
		public function main()
	Get Varialbes:
		public function main(array $getVars)


Model

	File Name:
		{name}.php
	Class Name:
		{name}_Model extends Base
	Loading from controller:
		$this->load_model('test');
	Usage:
		Test_model::testing();

	
Library
	File Name:
		{name}.php
	Class Name:
		{name}
	Loading from controller:
		$this->load_library('test_lib');
	Usage:
		test_lib::testing();


View
	Usage:
		$this->load_view('_header', $data);